title: Dana Kellin Crystal Silver Shade 5 Station Necklace
description:
Offset yet completely on the mark, Dana Kellin's 5 Station Swarovski Crystal Necklace is a subtle nod to sophisticated glamour. Dana Kellin jewelry is best known for its intricate, meticulous wire-wrapping details. The labor intensive, time consuming nature of the process results in a balance of organic, handmade charm with an air of refinement and sophistication.

  • Dimensions: 41.5 in necklace, stations from .5 in to 1.5 in.
  • Materials: 14/20 goldfill frames, wire, chain, Swarovski crystals
